text.tspan: Newest buffer is not yet written,
1) If most recent buffer is not written to:
1a) reading routine reads from most recent buffer
1b) otherwise from most recent but one
2) If buffer most recent buffer is not being read:
2a) writing routine writes to oldest buffer,
3) When writing routine is finished, buffer is inserted in front of stack, last one is removed
<- This should not happen with three buffers
